api oil inventory report to be issued tonight
    new york, april 21 - 
the american petroleum institute, api, said its weekly u.s. petroleum
inventory report will be issued tonight, despite many company closures
on friday of last week for the easter holiday. the api report is
usually released around 1700 edt on tuesday nights. the energy
information administration said it also expects its weekly oil
statistic report to be released as usual, on wednesday night at about
1700 edt. reuter 
